values: （用于提出意见或征求建议时）会；（表示预期或设想）就；（表示不曾发生或不可能存在的事）会；（说明动机）就会；（表示某人想要某物或想做某事）想；（表示客气地请求别人做某事）请…好吗；要不要…；过去老是；过去常常；（带出一贯的行为）总是；爱；<文>但愿…（表示强烈的愿望）；（表示推测或希望）也许；大概；（表示有充分理由猜测是某种情况）肯定；应该
将；将会；（will的过去式，用于转述）

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指过去经常发生的行为，主观感情色彩较浓，只表过去惯常行为，既不表状态也不表持续动作。不含“过去如此，现在不再这样”的意味。
指客观地表示过去的习惯，既可是过去经常发生的动作，又可是过去一向存在的状态，比would通俗，往往含今昔感。

bilingual.target: 那将是一个真正的成就。

bilingual.source: It would be so exciting if I could do that.
bilingual.target: 如果我能做到，那将是非常令人兴奋的。

bilingual.source: In addition, it would provide 60 jobs for local people.
bilingual.target: 此外，它将为当地人提供60个工作岗位。

bilingual.source: They would travel to the edge of the world to catch the sun.
bilingual.target: 他们将前往世界的尽头去抓住太阳。

bilingual.source: The new shopping mall would offer the choice that they require.
bilingual.target: 新的购物中心将提供他们需要的选择。

bilingual.source: The world would be a little less amazing if the hellbender went extinct.
bilingual.target: 如果大鲵灭绝了，世界将少一些奇妙。

bilingual.source: Kenya announced that it would export much more crude oil per day the next year.
bilingual.target: 肯尼亚宣布明年每天将出口更多的原油。

bilingual.source: The doctor explained how the incision would be made.
bilingual.target: 医生解释了切口将如何进行。

bilingual.source: She declared that she would participate in the competition.
bilingual.target: 她宣布自己将参加比赛。

bilingual.source: The statement was construed to mean that he would resign.
bilingual.target: 这句话被解释为他将辞职。

list.abstract: would（Britain）：[wud] would（US）：[wud]，在陈述语气中，表示过去将来时，表示有意识的行动或意志，常用于间接引语中）将；要；偏要；愿； (would like to do sth) 想做某事

yingyinNormal.en: The consequences for the one responsible would be severe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 进行这些事的人将必须承担严重的后果。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: It would put more money in workers' pockets. It would help 28 million Americans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这将让雇员的腰包鼓起来。这将帮助2800万的国人。

yingyinNormal.en: All of the beauty you and I have made in this place, the art of it, they would have destroyed it. They would have destroyed you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在这里共同创造的美丽，还有其中的艺术，他们会将其摧毁，他们会将你摧毁。

yingyinNormal.en: And everyone whoever doubted me would be watching and they would be crying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 任何曾经质疑过我的人都将目睹这一切，而流下羡慕嫉妒恨的眼泪。

yingyinNormal.en: And one of the best would be to raise the minimum wage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其中最好的一个办法将是提高最低工资标准。

yingyinNormal.en: Because as you approached it, you wouldn't be pulled enough and would merely pass by with your path slightly bent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为，当地球靠近太阳时，将没有足够的引力将地球拉回，而就只是沿着切线方向离去。

yingyinNormal.en: One that would transform him into the world's first super soldier.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个项目会将他变成世界上第一位超级战士。

yingyinNormal.en: She's injured. Any results would be unclear. You can get rid of her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她受伤了，测试结果将受影响，你来处理她。

yingyinNormal.en: And it would mean a lot to me to have my big brother at my wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我的大哥能出席我婚礼那将对我意义非常重大。

yingyinNormal.en: If the Mockingjay was gone, the rebels would already be using her as a martyr.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果嘲笑鸟死了，叛军将把她当作烈士追颂。

yingyinNormal.en: It would make it harder to move health workers and supplies back and forth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这将让医疗工作者和物资的来往变得更加困难。

yingyinNormal.en: How much domestic workforce would you anticipate shedding as a result of this merger?
yingyinNormal.zh: 由于这次兼并，你预计将辞退多少国内员工？

yingyinNormal.en: I would like to award you the highest honor I can bestow. The Ellie badge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我将授予你象征最高的荣誉的"Ellie徽章"。

yingyinNormal.en: It would be an excellent way to meet new friends. You could invite the militia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那将是认识新朋友最好的方式，你可以邀请民兵们。

yingyinNormal.en: I guess I should've known that's what I would become for you, just another memory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许我早该知道，我之于你，将不过是另一段记忆。

yingyinNormal.en: And what if you didn't talk to them for two weeks? They would be gone forever and would never be willing to date you again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你两周没有和他们聊天，你将永远失去他们，因为他们不会再想和你约会。

yingyinNormal.en: He says humans would only see you as the enemy. He wants me to roll you back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说人类只会将你视为敌人，他想让我对你进行回滚操作。

yingyinNormal.en: But we would never make any major decisions without consulting your generals first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是不先咨询你的上将们，我们将不会做出任何重大决定。

yingyinNormal.en: But what would have happened if I had said C? Consumer applications for genomics, they will flourish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我选的是C呢？基因组学的消费需求将大大增加。

yingyinNormal.en: That would seem likely, however, if the president's wounds are as serious as we believe them to be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果总统的伤势如我们认为的那样严重，这将很有可能。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: But both these criteria <highlight>would</highlight> be at the expense of time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但这两个标准都将以时间为代价。

examination_example.sentence: A move back to self-sufficiency, the argument goes, <highlight>would</highlight> boost the farming industry, political sovereignty and even the nation's health.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种观点认为，回归自给自足将促进农业发展、政治主权甚至国家健康。

examination_example.sentence: But it doesn't necessarily follow from findings like these that a world without work <highlight>would</highlight> be filled with unease.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但从这些发现中并不一定得出这样的结论：一个没有工作的世界会充满不安。

examination_example.sentence: Being a good parent is, of course, what every parent <highlight>would</highlight> like to be.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当然，每个父母都想成为一个好父母。

examination_example.sentence: Still, while every parent <highlight>would</highlight> like to be patient, this is no easy task.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管每个父母都想要有耐心，但这并非易事。

examination_example.sentence: It can be learned from Paragraph 1 that the biotech companies <highlight>would</highlight> like genes to be patentable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从第一段可以了解到，生物技术公司希望基因可以获得专利。

examination_example.sentence: We plan to have a future where a lot of <highlight>would</highlight>-be workers do not get left behind.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们计划有这样一个将来，许多未来的工人不会被抛在后面。

examination_example.sentence: Hindrance to the reform of the legal system originates from the stern exam for <highlight>would</highlight>-be lawyers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 法律制度改革的障碍源于对未来律师的严格考试。

examination_example.sentence: Which of the following measures <highlight>would</highlight> the Productivity Commission support?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 生产力委员会会支持以下哪项措施？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: If so we have a vacancy in our team which <highlight>would</highlight> suit you.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果是这样的话，我们团队有个空缺适合你。

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>would</highlight> involve traveling overseas.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这将涉及到海外旅行。

examination_example.sentence: If anyone had told me three years ago that I <highlight>would</highlight> be spending most of my weekends camping.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果三年前有人告诉我的话，我会把大部分周末都花在露营上。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Would</highlight> you like to see them?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你想见见他们吗？

examination_example.sentence: Which one <highlight>would</highlight> you like?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你想要哪一个？

examination_example.sentence: If you are a fruit grower—or <highlight>would</highlight> like to become one—take advantage of Apple Day to see what's around.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你是一名果农——或者想成为一名果农——那就利用“苹果节”来了解下相关情况吧。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: She was called an alien and some kids <highlight>would</highlight> even steal her snacks.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她被称为外星人，有些孩子甚至会偷她的零食。

examination_example.sentence: When I was talking with the cashier (收银员), he asked what I <highlight>would</highlight> be doing with this little tree.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我和收银员交谈时，他问我要这棵小树做什么。

examination_example.sentence: Roy thought the doctor <highlight>would</highlight> hurt him so he was afraid.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 罗伊认为医生会伤害他，所以他很害怕。

sense_info_list.en: indicating the consequence of an imagined event or situation

examination_example.sentence: He argued with the rich man, hoping the rich man <highlight>would</highlight> keep his promise.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他和富人争论，希望富人能遵守诺言。

examination_example.sentence: They told the reporter that they <highlight>would</highlight> continue at the end of next year if they had the chance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们告诉记者，如果有机会，他们将在明年年底继续工作。

examination_example.sentence: I don't think there <highlight>would</highlight> be enough jobs for everyone in a garden.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我认为花园里没有足够的工作给每个人。

examination_example.sentence: Because I think her suggestions are helpful and I <highlight>would</highlight> like to have a try.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为我觉得她的建议很有帮助，我想试一试。

examination_example.sentence: Today I <highlight>would</highlight> like to introduce some simple but useful ways that we can follow easily in our daily life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今天我想介绍一些简单但有用的方法，我们在日常生活中可以轻松照着做。

examination_example.sentence: I <highlight>would</highlight> also like to visit you at your home on the fourth of August.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我还想在8月4号去你家拜访你。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Would</highlight> you please repeat what you said?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 请你重复一下你说的话好吗？

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Would</highlight> you please tell me who the robot belongs to?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你能告诉我这个机器人是属于谁的吗？

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Would</highlight> you mind giving me some advice?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你介意给我一些建议吗？

sense_info_list.en: expressing a conjecture, opinion, or hope

examination_example.sentence: What <highlight>would</highlight> be the best title for the text?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这篇课文最好的标题是什么？

examination_example.sentence: What <highlight>would</highlight> be the best title for the passage?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这篇文章最好的标题是什么？

examination_example.sentence: Based on its body size, a bat like the greater mouse-eared bat <highlight>would</highlight> be expected to live four years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据它的体型，像鼠耳蝙蝠这样的蝙蝠预计能活四年。

sense_info_list.en: used to make a comment about behaviour

examination_example.sentence: Each time I <highlight>would</highlight> answer softly, "It's me, Ray, Grandpa!"
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每次我都会轻声回答：“是我，雷，爷爷！”

examination_example.sentence: I <highlight>would</highlight> sit for hours by the river doing nothing-simply daydreaming.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我总是会在河边坐几个小时，什么也不做，只是做白日梦。

word_usage.usage:
表示“宁愿…而不愿…；与其…宁可…”的意思时，可用"would rather…than…."或"would...rather than..."的句型，中间省略号部分只能接动词原形，不能接动词不定式或动名词形式。
示例：(1) I would rather watch TV at home than go to the cinema. 
我宁可在家看电视而不愿去看电影。 
(2) The children would walk there rather than take a bus. 
孩子们宁愿步行去那里而不愿乘公共汽车。

would作will的过去式，与动词原形构成过去将来时，多用于第二、第三人称。
示例：He said he would come.
他说他会来。
